引发巨大反响，就在于跟社会情绪「接驳」。这会倒逼更多互联网企业正视畸形加班文化的弊端，及时转变用工思路。「996」是互联网行业用工史上的一段弯路 -- 经济·科技 -- 人民网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-31a092e05a2f366c2bbee244715902cf_720w.jpeg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "269 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/485677516"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IwvLqv6fn0u4hEAMaCDcwMjEwMTI2IKfV5YkGMCU4nwRAEnIJNDg1Njc3NTE2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1631257328.2251554", "card_id": "Q_485367822", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 33}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《天龙八部》中有什么不起眼但很妙的情节和设定？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-e8ff85c77b496f2174b268b872d11461_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "245 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/485367822"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IwvLqv6fn0u4hEAMaCDcwMTQxNDMyINug3YkGMAE4rwFAE3IJNDg1MzY3ODIyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1631257328.2256033", "card_id": "Q_485900229", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 30}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "世预赛阿根廷 3:0 击败玻利维亚 ，梅西戴帽超贝利加冕南美国家队射手王，如何评价这场比赛？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "2022 年世界杯预选赛南美区第 10 轮，阿根廷 3:0 完胜玻利维亚。梅西上演「帽子戏法」，他也就此以 79 球的数据超越了巴西传奇球星贝利，成为了国家队进球数最多的南美球员。世预赛 - 梅西帽子戏法 +79 球超越贝利! 阿根廷 3-0 大胜"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-d47aaaded9dbc46981a1216a6d4b6914_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "189 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/485900229"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IwvLqv6fn0u4hEAMaCDcwMjU5NDAyIJLz6okGMAI4fkAUcgk0ODU5MDAyMjl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id":